info.name: run-aspnetcore-microservices
info.description: Microservices on .Net platforms which used Asp.Net Web API, Docker, RabbitMQ, MassTransit, Grpc, Ocelot API Gateway, MongoDB, Redis, PostgreSQL, SqlServer, Dapper, Entity Framework Core, CQRS and Clean Architecture implementation. Also includes Cross-Cutting concerns like Implementing Centralized Distributed Logging with Elasticsearch, Kibana and SeriLog, use the HealthChecks with Watchdog, Implement Retry and Circuit Breaker patterns with Polly and so on.. See Microservices Architecture and Step by Step Implementation on .NET Course w/ discount->
